  "body": "Forked from https://github.com/containerd/cri/issues/679.\r\n\r\nGRPC 4M default MaxMsgSize limit may not be enough, especially when container runtime spec and extension are large.\r\n\r\nAnd we'll get:\r\n```\r\ngrpc: received message larger than max (4659741 vs. 4194304): unknown\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis is not a problem for cri plugin because we've removed the grpc layer, but this is still a problem to other containerd users.",
